# === Dataset Privacy ===
# The canonical dataset is argumentation_analysis/data/extract_sources.json.gz.enc
# (encrypted, tracked). Any plaintext/decrypted/downstream form must stay out of git.
# See CLAUDE.md "Dataset Privacy Discipline".
Arg_Semantic_Index/sources/*.json
Arg_Semantic_Index/sources/*.jsonl
*_unencrypted*
*_decrypted*
extract_sources.json
extract_sources_*.json
!extract_sources.json.gz.enc
